  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为L++覆盖率分析器设计一个状态图，核心是要体现从空闲到加载、追踪、分析、报告输出的完整工作流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "loaded",
        "tracking",
        "analyzing",
        "reporting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这个分析器是基于blueprint工作的吧？初始状态应该是idle，然后通过LOAD进入loaded状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "loaded",
        "LOAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但有个前提条件——只有当blueprint为None时，idle才能通过LOAD进入loaded。如果已经加载了，再次LOAD应该停留在loaded状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "loaded",
        "LOAD",
        "blueprint"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了从idle到loaded的LOAD转换，以及loaded自身的自循环LOAD。接下来从loaded怎么进入追踪阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "loaded",
        "LOAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通过START操作，但前提是blueprint已经存在。另外我们还支持IMPORT操作，也能从loaded进入tracking，同样需要blueprint不为空。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loaded",
        "tracking",
        "START",
        "IMPORT",
        "blueprint"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "注意到IMPORT有两个来源？从loaded到tracking的IMPORT，条件里写了两遍blueprint is not None，这是笔误还是特殊含义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loaded",
        "tracking",
        "IMPORT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "是笔误，应该是blueprint is not None && coverage_data is not None，从loaded导入时需要两者都存在。但tracking状态自身的IMPORT只需要blueprint存在即可。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loaded",
        "tracking",
        "IMPORT",
        "coverage_data"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在tracking状态有多个自循环：STATE、TRANSITION、GATE、ACTION、EVENT，这些是追踪过程中的不同操作类型对吧？",
