      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，tracking阶段就是持续追踪这些元素。当用户想分析时，从tracking通过ANALYZE进入analyzing状态，条件是coverage_data不为空。",
      "elements_involved": [
