      "utterance": "我发现loaded也可以直接ANALYZE到analyzing，条件只是blueprint存在。这和从tracking过去的条件不同，需要都保留吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loaded",
        "analyzing",
        "ANALYZE",
        "blueprint"
